Total order is incompatible with humanity; if caused, brings sadness and must be fixed.

Tentative plot: 
AI created to bring order to stuff;
AI can control biological beings;
AI let loose on an area;
sadness ensues;
protagonists try to reason with AI;
almost get converted;
seek weakness and exploit it;
AI shuts down;
victims of control are sad at what happened


Setting prerequisites:
AI tech;
biotech with mind control;
someone thinking it a good idea to combine
